1 0 0 1 54 233 Tm (Nepal. Its main job is to take a loan application, read the applicant's documents, estimate) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 219 Tm (income from alternative data sources, calculate a repayment score, check compliance rules, and) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
